DEPENDENCIES
~~~~~~~~~~~~
 * Python2.5+

INSTALLATION
~~~~~~~~~~~~

    $ gunzip -c tnote-x.x.x.tar.gz | tar x
    $ cd tnote-x.x.x
    $ sudo python setup.py 


